body:
poor whistling man. just minding his own business walking home to his wife and kids when all of a sudden he was mugged by some random white kid with goggles. knowing how dangerous the streets of zaun are he immediately defends himself and fatally wounds the kid. just one shot. not like he was trying to kill him, he just wanted to get the this mugger off him so he could go home safely. 

next thing you know a black kid comes out of no where and kills the poor whistler for defending himself against a mugging. &quot;you dare defend yourself against a mugging?!?!? I KEEL YOU!&quot;

typical gang violence if you ask me. whistler was at the wrong place at the wrong time. RIP.
